name: Amur Tigro
description:
Amur Tigro is a respected fighter from Asia. He has fought in several countries, and he has earned the title of "the invincible". Not because he was the strongest, but because he never gave up. He always got back on his feet even after being knocked down.

Amur Tigro's whereabouts are currently unknown. Has he finally been beaten down and defeated? Or was he on the hunt to take down his greatest enemy?
